          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"almasim-end-to-end-archive-pipeline\">ALMASim End-to-End Archive Pipeline</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">This notebook walks through the full workflow:</span>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Query</strong> ALMA metadata via TAP</li>\n<li><strong>Resolve</strong> DataLink product URLs for selected observations</li>\n<li><strong>Download</strong> raw data products (parallel, multi-mirror)</li>\n<li><strong>Unpack</strong> ASDM archives into raw MeasurementSets</li>\n<li><strong>Calibrate</strong> raw MSs using delivered calibration scripts</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote>\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Note:</strong> Steps 4 and 5 require <code>casatools</code> and <code>casatasks</code>\n(<code>pip install \"almasim[casa]\"</code>), which are Linux-only packages.\nSteps 1\u20133 run on any platform.</span>\n</blockquote></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
